npm init
npm i express cors
npm i -d  @types/express @types/node nodemon typescript
tsc - convert ts ext.file to js.ext file
if dont have tsc command, type npm i -g typescript

split bash commands into 3 and run tsc-w , npm start and leave the last bash for installation
tsc -w  will do a real-time update for the .ts file to .js file


To connect to database
npm install typeorm --save
npm install reflect-metadata --save
npm install @types/node --save -dev
npm install mysql --save

ormconfig.json - logging: true will show all the logs that you have done 